name: LIMPEH (person umbrella bed)
description:
An original Gory Orgy animated loop. 10 seconds. 1228X1228, H264, 2021
LIMPEH is a multi-layered animation that utilises more than one machine-learning model. A fleshy, shape-shifting mass (computer generated erotica) is conspicuously analysed by a machine-learning model that identifies people and objects. LIMPEH (person umbrella bed) is one of three. One copy is retained by the artist, while the other two are available for purchase. Gory Orgy is the experimental machine-learning project by kiwi artist and film-maker Ed Lust.
